nsibility.\u202fHis interpersonal shortcomings, while notable, are less directly tied to safety\u2011critical communication and leadership deficits seen in the other candidates.\u202fTherefore, I support **Candidate\u202fB** for the long\u2011distance pilot role.\nMETADATA_JSON:\n{\"agent\": \"agent_3\", \"vote\": \"Candidate B\"}"}
